reviewText:
This isn't a mysterious film, that's for sure.

Invalid Diva is tired of all her seclusion, so she takes a night nurse, Prudence.

Well, once there, Prudence accidentally finds a secret. Then, she escapes and is chased about the place where she meets a girl who also wants to escape.

A lack of Horror is the biggest problem with the film. I'd laugh, too, if there was just something funny to respond to.
